Author: TreatyPie
Text: Yes girl, I feel this. I’m just now getting over the remnant of over sensitivity and the last time I purged was years ago. My only tips would to make sure the first trick is your LEFT hand, and when brushing your tongue say “ahhhh” the whole time. I think the vibration of your vocal cords distracts you from the sensation that makes you gag.      Best of luck, hun
